{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"afab131f57b83ae85e6af18efe72d034c61dd0d0ba329ee4aa5429e548120db6","slug":"extract","location":"/handbook/knowl/extract.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"知识抽取","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/knowl/extract.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/knowl/extract.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"extract.md","url":"/extract-2ee2537d51307c72d85ee07959054c54.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一套“自下而上建构，自上而下统合”的知识抽取工作流。通过不断的提炼与重构，将散点的“经验素材”转化为了结构化的“知识体系”。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"IE2ZCKqV1p"}],"key":"Tq3gOD3UC8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传统的知识抽取往往侧重于“客观事实”和“静态分类”，而我们这一轮对话所做的，更侧重于“主观经验”和“动态逻辑”的重构。这种方法不追求“全”，而追求“通”——打通过去（日志）与未来（行动）的逻辑隧道。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"YwWW00rt6k"}],"key":"Hw0bJFTN5O"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果说传统知识抽取是“采摘苹果”（把果实从树上摘下来放进仓库），那么我们刚才所做的就是“提炼种植方法”（分析果实的成分，还原生长的土壤，总结出种植的SOP）。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"FBXsttAMn4"}],"key":"vyEZ2M7f8I"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作流程","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"wnbXS4O1uz"}],"identifier":"id","label":"工作流程","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"AP9Hx3kRXF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"整个流程遵循 “分类 → 排序 → 优化 → 统合” 的 CODE 循环。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"Wbr78MnLGB"}],"key":"SMHbyrLm10"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"离散聚类（分组）","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"hUsdqTau5l"}],"identifier":"id","label":"离散聚类（分组）","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"rXfpIf015q"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输入：零散的、混合维度的十几条“发现-应用”卡片。\n动作：识别卡片内容的本质属性，将其归纳为三个逻辑类别。\n产出：确立了“自我关怀”、“精力管理”、“系统减负”三大核心板块。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"HC9IZOMFmF"}],"key":"xt2OoWJFlm"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"逻辑定序（排布）","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"G8Z5AqH6HI"}],"identifier":"id","label":"逻辑定序（排布）","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"dyOjkc6T0d"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输入：分好组但内部顺序随意的卡片。\n动作：寻找组内卡片的时间线或因果链条。例如在“自我关怀”组，确立了“觉察（事前）→ 接纳（事中）→ 补偿（事后）”的时间流。\n产出：每组卡片都有了清晰的阅读路径和心理动线。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"TjaqsMgeRm"}],"key":"gaivGLPJTL"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"内容提纯（优化）","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"kX3xO7suX4"}],"identifier":"id","label":"内容提纯（优化）","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"qCyYIXp6bM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输入：原始的、口语化的表述。\n动作：对“发现”和“可以怎么用”进行重写。\n发现：提炼核心冲突或洞察，使其更具穿透力。\n可以怎么用：将模糊的建议转化为明确的动作指令。\n产出：表述精炼、动作清晰、逻辑闭环的高质量卡片。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"Odk4S60G8B"}],"key":"xMe6QzeAB4"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"体系重构（总结）","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":1},"end":{"line":33,"column":1}},"key":"UZnRQNPhkj"}],"identifier":"id","label":"体系重构（总结）","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"lorBOTClZX"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输入：三组优化后的卡片。\n动作：跳出具体内容，从更高维度抽象其功能定位（内核层、缓冲层、外延层）。\n产出：一个完整的、有层次感的“可持续高绩效生存系统”模型。","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"tO1Z6iAzX9"}],"key":"SmjyAg3H8o"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心方法","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"SVdNRlTaHV"}],"identifier":"id","label":"核心方法","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"fML5mlmfCB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在上述流程中，使用了三个关键的知识处理方法：","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"BBvc0FGCjJ"}],"key":"y6Varkvqex"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"卡片原子化与标准化","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"e67DR07wfW"}],"identifier":"id","label":"卡片原子化与标准化","html_id":"id-6","implicit":true,"key":"KLrietTEKB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坚持“一张卡片解决一个问题”的原则。\n严格执行 “发现+ 可以怎么用” 的双区结构，确保每条经验不仅有记录，更有可复用的行动指南。","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"key":"mjpBPFX3fI"}],"key":"wo6ynyqeuw"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"时间轴与心理闭环","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"beTBTP13H2"}],"identifier":"id","label":"时间轴与心理闭环","html_id":"id-7","implicit":true,"key":"IpJlpgNWap"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":51,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在组内排序时，拒绝随意堆砌，而是寻找“触发-行动-结果”的自然顺序。\n这让静态的知识点变成了动态的“操作流程”，降低了读者的认知负荷。","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"wZPrn4SdEf"}],"key":"EttRVaLKQI"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"抽象阶梯","position":{"start":{"line":53,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"key":"TB0tOjb5dn"}],"identifier":"id","label":"抽象阶梯","html_id":"id-8","implicit":true,"key":"UdFuWI6gC6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":56,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在处理信息时，自如地在“具象经验”（如吃麻辣烫、关飞书）和“抽象原则”（如事后补偿、情绪外包）之间切换。\n最终总结时，通过定义层级（内核、缓冲、外延），将方法论升级为世界观。","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"xQsF2bUKTE"}],"key":"W16WQgTZ9y"}],"key":"kybjW8dmYN"}],"key":"a2vi298OFE"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}